    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Agency Is Created For Health Business</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Patrick McGeehan</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Mcgeehan, Patrick</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>CommonHealth opens Noesis Healthcare Interactions, a new healthcare ad agency, in Morristown, NJ (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>CommonHealth in Parsippany, N.J., part of the WPP Group, is opening Noesis Healthcare Interactions in Morristown, N.J., a new healthcare agency with 43 employees and billings estimated at more than $49 million from clients like Novartis.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>CommonHealth in Parsippany, N.J., part of the WPP Group, is opening Noesis Healthcare Interactions in Morristown, N.J., a new healthcare agency with 43 employees and billings estimated at more than $49 million from clients like Novartis.</p>
        <p>Bruce Epstein, 36, is currently heading the agency as senior vice president and management supervisor; he had held the same title at Thomas Ferguson Associates, a sibling of Noesis.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
